            <li><strong>Digital communication:</strong> They should be comfortable receiving checklists, sending photos, and communicating via WhatsApp or a management app.</li>
            <li><strong>References from other hosts:</strong> Ask for at least two Airbnb hosts who can speak to the cleaner's reliability and quality.</li>
            <li><strong>Attention to hospitality details:</strong> Ask them what they do with toilet paper at the end of a turnover. The <a href="/blog/show-this-to-your-airbnb-cleaner-for-5-star-reviews" style="color: var(--color-primary-dark); text-decoration: underline;">toilet paper fold</a> is a small but meaningful test of whether they think like an Airbnb host.</li>
