          <p>Require your cleaner to send a photo of every room after completing the turnover. This takes under 5 minutes and creates a timestamped record of the property's condition at check-in. Review the photos remotely before confirming the unit is ready. Platforms like Turno (formerly TurnoverBnB) or simple WhatsApp photo shares both work well for this.</p>

