          <p>Visit the property in person at least once a month, arriving as if you were a guest: use the front door code, walk through each room with fresh eyes. What do you notice in the first 10 seconds? That's what your guests notice. Check under the bed, inside drawers, behind the toilet, and in the back corners of the fridge.</p>

