          <p>After every checkout, read the cleanliness rating the guest gave you in their private review data (available in your Airbnb host dashboard). Track it. If your cleanliness rating drops below 4.8 on any stay, review the check-in photo documentation and follow up with your cleaner to understand what happened. Treat each review as data, not just feedback.</p>

